{"tid":2381264,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"工聯會指三成一會員失業或放無薪假","createTime":"2021-01-26T12:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T11:29:03.000Z","uid":39464,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"9badd294d08f0a212cfcc1f9dff92a509dfce8ff","tid":2381264,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T12:21:34.000Z","msg":"工聯會指，失業情況最嚴重的是建造業、飲食業及零售業，估計失業率很大機會超越沙士時的8.7%，半年內亦不會有明顯改善，希望政府成立150億元的緊急失業援助金。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會在去年12月至本月初以網上問卷，訪問超過1.7萬名會員，當中一成八人正在失業，過半已經失業超過半年，兩成三人更已失業超過一年，另外有一成四人需要放無薪假，四成九受訪者認為，自己的積蓄不足以支持三個月的開支。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=421793\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D421793&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSvwHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=f0a4986d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D421793&h=7912ca6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=421793</a>"},{"pid":"4688d6a0339c5cfe5362838b8d1089f84ba32b50","tid":2381264,"uid":10905,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T12:23:14.000Z","msg":"咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c22c6dfe846ee64b2bd70f7f56ea96d4e59d2f7","tid":2381264,"uid":77717,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T12:24:30.000Z","msg":"其他本身無業"},{"pid":"74adededa219a1260207c0364e30da3d851ad9cb","tid":2381264,"uid":335434,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T12:26:04.000Z","msg":"全港失業率同就業不足率係6.6%同3.4% 工賊會全體會員失業率係31%<br />\n<br />\n結論：退出工賊會係保住份工或者重投就業市場嘅第一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee41e8237a937b0f0a518e0f6c92d3d23129a05","tid":2381264,"uid":52358,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T12:27:19.000Z","msg":"donki好多人<br />\n恆指三萬點<br />\n買樓要排隊<br />\n歡迎補充<img src=\"/assets/fa